Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_")
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "'"
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_")
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "'"
' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
